<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='540520' id='t-540520'>of creating a new voice for myself.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='543480' id='t-543480'>I was thrust into a world
I didn't quite know how to function in.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='547840' id='t-547840'>I stopped going to the care home</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='549520' id='t-549520'>and managed to get my first job
making photocopies.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='553400' id='t-553400'>As simple as this may sound,
it was amazing.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='556880' id='t-556880'>My new world was really exciting</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='558920' id='t-558920'>but often quite overwhelming
