<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='647680' id='t-647680'>However, after all I had been through,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='650480' id='t-650480'>I still couldn't shake the belief</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='652240' id='t-652240'>that nobody could truly see
