<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='655480' id='t-655480'>and accept me for who I am.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:09
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='658080' id='t-658080'>I also really struggled
to comprehend that I was a man.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='662280' id='t-662280'>The first time someone
referred to me as a man,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='665120' id='t-665120'>it stopped me in my tracks.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='667440' id='t-667440'>I felt like looking around
