<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='672080' id='t-672080'>That all changed with Joan.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='674280' id='t-674280'>We have an amazing connection</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='675880' id='t-675880'>and I learned how important it is
