<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='685520' id='t-685520'>I started to feel whole again,
a man worthy of love.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:40
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='689840' id='t-689840'>I began to reshape my destiny.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='692320' id='t-692320'>I spoke up a little more at work.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='694560' id='t-694560'>I asserted my need for independence
to the people around me.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='698960' id='t-698960'>Being given a means of communication
