<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='702840' id='t-702840'>I used the power of words and will
to challenge the preconceptions</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='707080' id='t-707080'>of those around me
and those I had of myself.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:01
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='710680' id='t-710680'>Communication is what makes us human,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='713400' id='t-713400'>enabling us to connect
on the deepest level</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='715720' id='t-715720'>with those around us --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='717680' id='t-717680'>telling our own stories,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='719280' id='t-719280'>expressing wants, needs and desires,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='722920' id='t-722920'>or hearing those of others
by really listening.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='726080' id='t-726080'>All this is how the world
knows who we are.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='729440' id='t-729440'>So who are we without it?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:23
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='732480' id='t-732480'>True communication increases understanding</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='735680' id='t-735680'>and creates a more caring
and compassionate world.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='739800' id='t-739800'>Once, I was perceived
to be an inanimate object,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='742920' id='t-742920'>a mindless phantom
of a boy in a wheelchair.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='746240' id='t-746240'>Today, I am so much more.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='748520' id='t-748520'>A husband, a son, a friend,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='750960' id='t-750960'>a brother, a business owner,
a first-class honors graduate,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='755240' id='t-755240'>a keen amateur photographer.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='757600' id='t-757600'>It is my ability to communicate
that has given me all this.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:53
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='762320' id='t-762320'>We are told that actions
speak louder than words.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='766040' id='t-766040'>But I wonder,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='768000' id='t-768000'>do they?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='770880' id='t-770880'>Our words, however we communicate them,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='773560' id='t-773560'>are just as powerful.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='775680' id='t-775680'>Whether we speak the words
with our own voices,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='778440' id='t-778440'>type them with our eyes,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='779800' id='t-779800'>or communicate them non-verbally
to someone who speaks them for us,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='784080' id='t-784080'>words are among our most powerful tools.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:19
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='788400' id='t-788400'>I have come to you through
a terrible darkness,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='791240' id='t-791240'>pulled from it by caring souls</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='793360' id='t-793360'>and by language itself.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='795720' id='t-795720'>The act of you listening to me today
brings me farther into the light.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='799760' id='t-799760'>We are shining here together.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='802080' id='t-802080'>If there is one most difficult obstacle
