<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='812680' id='t-812680'>It all sounds the same.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='814960' id='t-814960'>But if you will,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='816400' id='t-816400'>please imagine these next two words
